    title: 'Navigating Health Insurance for HIV Care: A Step-by-Step Guide',
    excerpt: 'How to understand your coverage, manage premiums, and access financial assistance for HIV medications and services.',
    category: 'Services',
    author: 'Elena Rodriguez, MSW',
